---
title: France's Cheesy French Onion Burger with French Fries and Baby Leaf Salad
description: "Allez les Bleus!" Show your support this Six Nations with burgers inspired by each team's homeland! An homage to French bistros, this Cheesy French Onion Burger is best served pitch-side with French fries and a baby leaf salad.
